# Configuração de CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) mais segura
# Substitua "https://seu-dominio-admin.com" pelo seu domínio real do painel
Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "https://painel.agency"
Header set Access-Control-Allow-Credentials "true"
Header set Access-Control-Allow-Methods "GET, POST, OPTIONS"
Header set Access-Control-Allow-Headers "Content-Type, Authorization"